Changelog

Source: NEWS.md

FWSAkRDRtools 0.2.0

Added

  • find.projects(): find projects on the USFWS Alaska Regional Data Repository (RDR)

  • Arguments to review local duplicate files and overwrite RDR files in commit.files()

  • Arguments to specify header and na strings in read.tables()

  • FWSAkRDRtools Tutorial article

FWSAkRDRtools 0.1.0

Improved the efficiency of find.files(), summarize.files() & read.tables().

FWSAkRDRtools 0.0.2

Minor bugs in find.files(), download.files(), read.tables(), and commit.files().

FWSAkRDRtools 0.0.1

Initial release of get.dir.template(), clone.project(), find.files(), download.files(), read.tables(), commit.files(), and summarize.files().
